  "question": [
    "The magnetic field at the centre of a circular coil of radius R carrying current I is 64 times the magnetic field at a distance x on its axis from the centre of the coil. Then the value of x is"
  ],
  "choices": [
    [
      "<katex>$\\frac{R}{4}\\sqrt{15}$</katex>"
    ],
    [
      "<katex>$R\\sqrt{3}$</katex>"
    ],
    [
      "<katex>$\\frac{R}{4}$</katex>"
    ],
    [
      "<katex>$R\\sqrt{15}$</katex>"
    ]
  ],
  "correctAnswer": 2,
  "explanation": [
    "<katex>$B_{center} = \\frac{\\mu_0 I}{2R}$</katex>, <katex>$B_{axis} = \\frac{\\mu_0 I R^2}{2(R^2+x^2)^{3/2}}$</katex>.",
    "<katex>$\\frac{B_{center}}{B_{axis}} = (1 + \\frac{x^2}{R^2})^{3/2} = 64$</katex>.",
    "<katex>$(1 + \\frac{x^2}{R^2}) = (64)^{2/3} = (4^3)^{2/3} = 16$</katex>.",
    "<katex>$\\frac{x^2}{R^2} = 15 \\implies x = R\\sqrt{15}$</katex>."
  ],
  "years": [
    2024
  ]
}